[
  {
    "text": "[clucking]",
    "start": 0.5,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "You're up, Casey.\nTruth or dare?",
    "start": 2.035,
    "duration": 2.368
  },
  {
    "text": "Hmm... Truth.",
    "start": 4.837,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, what's your\nmost embarrassing secret?",
    "start": 6.306,
    "duration": 2.969
  },
  {
    "text": "Aww, okay, my most embarrassing\nsecret is...",
    "start": 9.409,
    "duration": 4.337
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm the Mystery Stinker!",
    "start": 14.013,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasping]\nNo way!",
    "start": 15.114,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "You stunk up the whole bus!",
    "start": 16.282,
    "duration": 2.035
  },
  {
    "text": "I still smell it sometimes.",
    "start": 18.884,
    "duration": 1.903
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll never eat meatloaf again.",
    "start": 22.121,
    "duration": 2.269
  },
  {
    "text": "[clears throat]\nOkay, Sameer, truth or dare?",
    "start": 24.524,
    "duration": 3.603
  },
  {
    "text": "- Dare.\n- I dare you to...",
    "start": 28.26,
    "duration": 3.004
  },
  {
    "text": "run backwards\nuntil your next turn.",
    "start": 31.397,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh...",
    "start": 33.632,
    "duration": 1.301
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 35.167,
    "duration": 1.169
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah! Oops.",
    "start": 36.469,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry, Breakfast Bot.",
    "start": 37.47,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, I'll make another round.",
    "start": 39.004,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "[squawks] Hey,\nBreakfast Bot, you got Wi-Fi?",
    "start": 41.374,
    "duration": 2.903
  },
  {
    "text": "I need to message Priscilla.",
    "start": 44.41,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Beat it, use your own phone.",
    "start": 46.478,
    "duration": 2.003
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't, she blocked my number.",
    "start": 48.614,
    "duration": 2.369
  },
  {
    "text": "[beeping]",
    "start": 51.116,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, truth.",
    "start": 52.952,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see...",
    "start": 54.086,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Tell us your most\nembarrassing secret ever!",
    "start": 55.521,
    "duration": 2.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh, okay.",
    "start": 58.758,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "Last week I had a dream...",
    "start": 61.027,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "that I married Artemis\nfrom lucha club.",
    "start": 63.563,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasping]",
    "start": 66.632,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "[squealing]",
    "start": 67.666,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "Was I there?",
    "start": 68.767,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, it was a dumb dream.",
    "start": 69.836,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "You guys better not tell anyone.",
    "start": 71.237,
    "duration": 1.869
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course not, Ronnie Anne.",
    "start": 73.239,
    "duration": 1.869
  },
  {
    "text": "Those are\nthe truth or dare rules.",
    "start": 75.274,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "We take them very seriously.",
    "start": 77.243,
    "duration": 2.269
  },
  {
    "text": "[in unison]\nMm-hm!",
    "start": 79.946,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "Ice cream time!",
    "start": 80.98,
    "duration": 1.935
  },
  {
    "text": "- Whoa!\n- Ah!",
    "start": 83.382,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "[clucking]",
    "start": 84.85,
    "duration": 1.269
  },
  {
    "text": "[bell ringing]",
    "start": 88.021,
    "duration": 1.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Look, everyone,\nhere comes the bride!",
    "start": 89.622,
    "duration": 3.838
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 93.593,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Your groom Artemis awaits you.",
    "start": 94.56,
    "duration": 3.237
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 97.93,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "Ay, chihuahua!",
    "start": 98.998,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "Are those doves?",
    "start": 101.7,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "[frustrated groaning]",
    "start": 103.536,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "Runaway bride!",
    "start": 105.138,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 106.806,
    "duration": 1.901
  },
  {
    "text": "[bell ringing]",
    "start": 108.841,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "How could you guys?!",
    "start": 110.143,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "I thought we were friends!",
    "start": 111.377,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Who broke the rules and texted\nmy secret to the whole school?",
    "start": 113.146,
    "duration": 3.203
  },
  {
    "text": "- It wasn't me.\n- I didn't do it.",
    "start": 116.849,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "I swear on my skateboard\nIt wasn't me.",
    "start": 118.885,
    "duration": 2.735
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, you're the only ones\nI told about my dream,",
    "start": 121.82,
    "duration": 2.603
  },
  {
    "text": "which means\nsomeone here is lying.",
    "start": 124.557,
    "duration": 2.602
  },
  {
    "text": "[in unison]\nHmm...",
    "start": 127.593,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "[both]\nHmm...",
    "start": 129.128,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "She's right.",
    "start": 130.796,
    "duration": 1.102
  },
  {
    "text": "Something here stinks.",
    "start": 132.131,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't look at me.",
    "start": 134.033,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "I didn't get the meatloaf today!",
    "start": 135.267,
    "duration": 1.568
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, I'm going to find out\nwho Unknown Caller is.",
    "start": 136.969,
    "duration": 3.871
  },
  {
    "text": "[humming]",
    "start": 145.611,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "Where's his phone?",
    "start": 147.88,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "Hmm...",
    "start": 151.684,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh? Oh, no! My masterpiece!",
    "start": 154.119,
    "duration": 2.804
  },
  {
    "text": "[muffled talking]",
    "start": 158.057,
    "duration": 1.235
  },
  {
    "text": "[notification sound]",
    "start": 159.826,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, I just got a text.",
    "start": 164.197,
    "duration": 2.302
  },
  {
    "text": "Casey's the one\nwho stunk up the bus",
    "start": 166.632,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "on the field trip\nto the aquarium.",
    "start": 168.734,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "He is the Mystery Stinker!",
    "start": 170.703,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 172.772,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no!\nUnknown Caller strikes again!",
    "start": 174.741,
    "duration": 3.136
  },
  {
    "text": "And clearly it's not you.",
    "start": 178.01,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "No, I'm just\nthe Mystery Stinker.",
    "start": 179.579,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "You eat one piece of meatloaf\nand your life is over.",
    "start": 182.248,
    "duration": 3.036
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll have to move towns,\nchange my name...",
    "start": 185.418,
    "duration": 2.903
  },
  {
    "text": "[sighs] I've always\nliked the name Julio.",
    "start": 188.454,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "I've got to get\nto the bottom of this.",
    "start": 190.79,
    "duration": 1.768
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna check\neveryone else's phone",
    "start": 192.692,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "to see who's sending\nthese messages.",
    "start": 194.793,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "- That's a great idea!\n- Ah!",
    "start": 196.596,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll help!",
    "start": 198.097,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasps]\nYes!",
    "start": 201.0,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "[both]\nHuh?",
    "start": 206.872,
    "duration": 1.102
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah!",
    "start": 209.742,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't see!",
    "start": 210.776,
    "duration": 1.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Turn down the potato!",
    "start": 211.911,
    "duration": 1.801
  },
  {
    "text": "Guess what, Sameer wears lifts\nin his shoes to make him taller!",
    "start": 214.88,
    "duration": 3.738
  },
  {
    "text": "And Nikki's afraid\nof sock puppets!",
    "start": 218.751,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 221.22,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "It couldn't have been\nthem, either.",
    "start": 223.522,
    "duration": 2.203
  },
  {
    "text": "[bell ringing]",
    "start": 226.526,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "I think Unknown Caller\nmight be Laird.",
    "start": 228.895,
    "duration": 2.835
  },
  {
    "text": "He's certainly\nacting suspicious.",
    "start": 231.864,
    "duration": 2.77
  },
  {
    "text": "[humming]",
    "start": 234.767,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, come on!",
    "start": 238.337,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "How do we get to his phone?",
    "start": 240.039,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "[gasps]\nLeave it to Sameer.",
    "start": 241.908,
    "duration": 2.201
  },
  {
    "text": "- Huh?\n- Yo, Laird, catch!",
    "start": 244.409,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh? [grunts]",
    "start": 247.079,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, dear!",
    "start": 248.213,
    "duration": 1.369
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, give that back!",
    "start": 250.016,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "Ah, I don't even\nplay sportsball!",
    "start": 251.25,
    "duration": 2.269
  },
  {
    "text": "[screaming]",
    "start": 253.919,
    "duration": 1.669
  },
  {
    "text": "Hoo-ah!",
    "start": 256.789,
    "duration": 1.101
  },
  {
    "text": "[panting]",
    "start": 258.023,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, got it.",
    "start": 259.992,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "[notification sound]\nHey, Laird just got a text.",
    "start": 261.527,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Laird picks his nose\nwith his feet.\"",
    "start": 263.83,
    "duration": 2.568
  },
  {
    "text": "It's not true!",
    "start": 266.899,
    "duration": 1.135
  },
  {
    "text": "[laughing]",
    "start": 269.001,
    "duration": 2.135
  },
  {
    "text": "Gross, and impressive.",
    "start": 271.57,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "Laird didn't do it, which means\nthe only person left is...",
    "start": 273.338,
    "duration": 4.139
  },
  {
    "text": "- Sid!\n- [screams]",
    "start": 278.644,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "You've been the one\ntexting our secrets!",
    "start": 280.045,
    "duration": 2.603
  },
  {
    "text": "- How could you?\n- Not cool!",
    "start": 282.781,
    "duration": 1.169
  },
  {
    "text": "I have to move towns now.",
    "start": 284.083,
    "duration": 1.601
  },
  {
    "text": "What? I swear I didn't do it.",
    "start": 285.818,
    "duration": 2.703
  },
  {
    "text": "These lips have been zipped.",
    "start": 288.654,
    "duration": 1.968
  },
  {
    "text": "But you're the only one who\nhasn't been totally humiliated",
    "start": 291.423,
    "duration": 3.904
  },
  {
    "text": "by an embarrassing secret.",
    "start": 295.461,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "[muffled talking]",
    "start": 297.096,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "That's because I only did\ndares during the game.",
    "start": 299.198,
    "duration": 2.836
  },
  {
    "text": "I would never betray your trust.",
    "start": 302.167,
    "duration": 2.069
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, I have to go.\nI'm late for dance class.",
    "start": 304.603,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "It's true,\nshe did only do dares.",
    "start": 307.507,
    "duration": 2.969
  },
  {
    "text": "Open your eyes, Ronnie Anne!",
    "start": 310.609,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "I think she's playing us,\nwe just need proof.",
    "start": 312.744,
    "duration": 3.171
  },
  {
    "text": "Hmm...",
    "start": 316.115,
    "duration": 1.268
  }
]